| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-0144 — Mass File Rename (alphv)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 32286ee6-761d-5aa2-8d47-5f8b1a874d31"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
